{
 "file": "_STGX1_1.bin",
 "source_size": 20060,
 "built_size": 21312,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1205",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "基林中佐、我们马上就要抵达SIDE6{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "15e829e9b7ef4eefba02efcce7bbe84fef4ce7c5ef2ae96eef2bef9eef62ef96ef9fe9cd00e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1250",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……怎么回事！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909e7f2e7bdef52efb8ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1280",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……基林中佐！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e829e9b7ef4eefbaef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12a6",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚……阿兹纳布尔大佐？『赤色彗星』{00}究竟有何贵干？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d60909e7d2e856e882e831e7e1bea3050ce9e9e89fe9b6b50d00e906ef2ce7cb8ae930e8d3050000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12dc",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是来阻止贵官行动的",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6efcfe8efe869e930ef92efd6ef30e7b4000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12ea",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贵官企图发动的核攻击、是对南极条约的{00}明确违反",
   "zh_hex": "15e9308febdaeb2de870ef30e7b4e8f39ee7cc02e7b6e7beebb8eacae9d4e9ace7b400ef39e88ceab2e87c00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1306",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "立即中止作战、掉头返回格拉纳达",
   "zh_hex": "15e86be855ef4ee869ef2fef2802e9d3e92eeba8ef52e824e7c2e882ef2b000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x133c",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……哼",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8b30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1343",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "SIDE6并未批准南极条约、使用核武{00}器应该没问题才对……？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef9eef62ef96ef9fe9cde957e8b4ed63e87aebb8eacae9d4e9ac02e83fefb3e8f3e8ec00e8c3e873e898e7d8e997ea12e836e7be0909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1383",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "问题不在于此！",
   "zh_hex": "15e997ea12e7b5ef29e879e7caef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1390",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "核的封印一旦解开、之后便是无止境的相{00}互轰炸！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8f3e7b4eb83ec4fefb6ebcde89de7fa02e7cde7fee8fae7b6e7dce869eb81e7b4e8b100e9f9eefce9c9ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13b6",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "立即让舰队掉头、返回格拉纳达去！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e86be855e7f9e7d4e7c9e9d3e92e02eba8ef52e824e7c2e882ef2be7ebef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13eb",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是基连总帅的直属",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e829e86ee881e9a6e7b4e875ea240000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13f8",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "轮不到你这突击机动军的人来对我发号施{00}令",
   "zh_hex": "15ebf4e7b5e7d7e7b8e7b9e8b6e7cce7e4ef30e7e0e7b4efb2efcfe7beefcce870e833eb8d00e94e0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x142e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "基林中佐！",
   "zh_hex": "15e829e9b7ef4eefbaef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1452",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "无论付出多大牺牲、都必须摧毁高达！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dce8dce97eefbee7e9efa5ea52ea5102e840e860e9a2efe5e97ce812ef2bef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1473",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你若执意阻挠、纵然你是基西莉亚少将的{00}直属……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7e7e9fcef3ce8efed6602e8e6e7efe7b8e7b6e829e7f8e81ee7d6eface84ae7b400e875ea24090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14b3",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "MS部队、展开！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efa7ef9eef70e7c902e989e7faef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14d8",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶……！只能应战了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de0909ef97ef32e7c6e873ef28e7baef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14ed",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我方也出动MS队！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccefb1e7c0efbeef30efa7ef9ee7c9ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1515",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "核导弹就搭载在基林中佐的旗舰上！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8f3ea4be946e7c5eb09eb1def29e829e9b7ef4eefbae7b4eb0be7d4ef4cef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1530",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "各机请优先击破那艘桑吉巴尔！",
   "zh_hex": "15e819e7e4e83ae9afb8e7ccc7e7b7eb18ea2be7d9e85be7e10600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1562",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对SIDE6的核攻击、无论如何都必须{00}阻止！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7beef9eef62ef96ef9fe9cde7b4e8f3ef67e7cc02e7dce8dce7f0efbce840e860e9a200e8efe869ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x157c",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拜托各位！",
   "zh_hex": "15e91ae7f4e819e834ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15ae",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15c0",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "高达的威力究竟有多大……{00}身为赤色彗星、你不会不知道吧……",
   "zh_hex": "15e812ef2be7b4e96bdae906ef2ce7cbe7e9be090900e88de7c1e9e9e89fe9b6b502e7b8e7b5e7e2e7b5e85ae82ae7d0090900000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1614",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我当然知道",
   "zh_hex": "1509098bc4e7efe85ae82a000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1620",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但即便如此、并非事事都可原谅",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbe855e8fae7f0e7ca02e957e8f0efb8efb8e840e7c4e8e4ec95000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x163f",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "基林中佐……身为军人、你已偏离了应走{00}的正道",
   "zh_hex": "15e829e9b7c0a30909e88de7c1e7e0b402e7b8ef3aeb4de901e7bae873e89000e7b4ef3be82a00000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x168e",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "SIDE6里、有友军……？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef9eef62ef96ef9fe9cdef3102e7cbe960e7e009090500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16b7",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是一支叫独眼巨人小队的特务部队",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6efb6e883e8c1e8eee90bea25efb2e83ee7c9e7b4e7cfe94fef70e7c9000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16e1",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是为查明新型高达的下落、基林中佐派出{00}的部队吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e7c1eae9ef39ef8ae977e812ef2be7b489e92a02e829e9b7c0a3e985af00e7b4cce7c9e7d00000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x171f",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1726",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "高达的下落已经查明、他们的任务本已结{00}束……",
   "zh_hex": "15e812ef2be7b4ef4de92aef3ae8b7eae9ef3902e80ce7bbe7b4e89ae94fefa6ef3ae86800e895090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1747",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可他们似乎、得知了基林中佐的核攻击计{00}划……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e80ce7bbe944e93302e80ae85ae7bae829e9b7ef4eefbae7b4e8f3ef67e7ccea5500ea740909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1763",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "声称『高达由我们亲手摧毁』",
   "zh_hex": "15ea8aea010ce812ef2be8a6efcce7bbe894ef66efe5e97c0d00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1794",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "联系不上吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ee941e7b5ef4ce80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17be",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们似乎已经展开行动、联络也已中断了",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbe944e933ef3ae8b7e989e7faefd6ef3002ef2eeb14e7c0ef3aef4ee982e7ba0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x181d",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哼……是被丢在最前线、弃之不顾的部队{00}啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b30909e7b6e7f1ebb0ef29e8c5ef51e91602e938e7cde7b5ea1fe7b4ef70e7c900e7c300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1833",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、夏亚大佐、您打算怎么办？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02ef37e7d6efa5efba02e835e7f5e889e7f2e7bde8ea050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x186a",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……总不能见死不救吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e881e7b5e7c6e85cef6ae7b5e8cae7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x187d",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说所属不同、可他们同样是吉翁公国的{00}军人",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ede7fbea24e7b5e85d02e7c4e80ce7bbe85de7dae7b6e7d9ee88e9a4a1e7b400e7e0b400000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18c0",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……说得对、我也赞成布拉德中佐的意见",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7ede80ae7be02efcce7c0ec3ee837e831e7c2e82cef4eefbae7b4ef3ce85c00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18d7",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "以少数兵力潜入SIDE6、与独眼巨人{00}小队取得联络",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f3eface914ef93efb0eb3ce891ef9eef62ef96ef9fe9cd02e832e8eee90bea25efb200e83ee7c9e987e80aef2eeb14000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18f2",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要告知他们核攻击已取消、他们就不会{00}再做出鲁莽之举",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae8e5e85ae80ce7bbe8f3ef67e7ccef3ae987e92802e80ce7bbe7c5e7b5e7e200e80be81cefbee8a2edb2e7cdea21000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x192f",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、我这就编组前往SIDE6的部队{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02efcce7b9e7c5ec89ea0def51e911ef9eef62ef96ef9fe9cde7b4ef70e7c900090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1961",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不、不必、SIDE6由我亲自前往",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b502e7b5e86002ef9eef62ef96ef9fe9cde8a6efcce894efb5ef51e911000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1998",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要大佐您亲自前去……吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2aefa5efbae835e894efb5ef51e7eb0909e80205000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19c4",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "潜入这种事我早已驾轻就熟、再加上我和{00}另外几人就足够了……",
   "zh_hex": "15eb3ce891e7b9e7d1efb8efcce963ef3ae953e990e7c5eb9202e80be854ef4cefcce7d300e99be8f7eaa5efb2e7c5ea1ee920e7ba09090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a2b",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、能否也让我加入其中？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7c6e9bbe7c0e7f9efcce854e891e8cfef4e0500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a60",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……卡多大尉？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e801e7e9efa5efc6050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a85",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "少数人的行动、我在所罗门也有过经验",
   "zh_hex": "15eface914efb2e7b4efd6ef3002efccef29e7fbe7ece90ce7c0e7cbef36e8b7ea9900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a9d",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "更何况、被遗弃在前线的士兵之苦、我最{00}清楚不过",
   "zh_hex": "15e952efbce8d002e7f1eba9e938ef29ef51e916e7b4ef64ef93e7cde9e602efcce8c500e995ebd3e7b5ef360000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ac2",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所罗门那样的惨剧、绝不能再重演……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7ece90ce7b7e7dae7b4ed5decb502e91ce7b5e7c6e80be8a1ea2f0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1af5",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……好吧、那就拜托卡多大尉同行了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c7e7d002e7b7e7c5e91ae7f4e801e7e9efa5efc6e85defd6e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b29",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b71",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真是的……！都这么天真……",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7b6e7b40909ef97e840e7b9e7bde844e8200909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b8b",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不过嘛、这样倒也不坏",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5ef36e93602e7b9e7dae848e7c0e7b5e9ed00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b9f",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那种隐秘行动、可是我们海兵队的拿手好{00}戏",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7d1eb73ecf5efd6ef3002e7c4e7b6efcce7bbe91bef93e7c9e7b4e9a7ef66e7c700ea3e000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bb8",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要交给我和德托洛夫、保准把人平安送{00}到",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae861e839efcce7d3e82ce7f4e94ae83002ea47e87ae81befb2e887e7fce9ba00e7d7000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c10",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那之后、情况有什么变化吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7cde7fe02e88be8d0e7cbe7dde7bde955e9a5e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c46",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……没有",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d8e7cb000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c50",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "载着核导弹的舰队、已经驶出格拉纳达",
   "zh_hex": "15eb1de86de8f3ea4be946e7b4e7d4e7c902ef3ae8b7e975efbee824e7c2e882ef2b0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c65",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "依旧朝着SIDE6航行中……大概就是{00}这么个情况",
   "zh_hex": "15eafceac8eaade86def9eef62ef96ef9fe9cde9c1efd6ef4e0909efa5ec76e7c5e7b600e7b9e7bde828e88be8d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1caa",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "都到了联邦舰队逼近阿·巴瓦·库的这个{00}节骨眼上了……吗",
   "zh_hex": "15e840e7d7e7baef2eefaae7d4e7c9ebf6efd8e7d2ef4be85be99fef4be9b3e7b4e7b9e82800ebeceb76e90bef4ce7ba0909e802000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cc9",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "吉翁……要败了啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d9ee880909ef2ae88fe7bae7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cfe",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是啊",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7c3000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d37",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这地方真不错啊、米莎",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef63efb1e820e7b5e885e7c302e878ef7c0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d6f",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是啊",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7c3000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d77",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要不是这种世道、真想在这儿住下来呢",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7b5e7b6e7b9e7d1e83ce82a02e820e7e6ef29e7b9eb7ce85989d9e907000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dbf",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "确实……",
   "zh_hex": "15e88ce87f09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e08",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……咦？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef49050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e10",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们俩、在这种地方做什么呢？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbeb7b02ef29e7b9e7d1ef63efb1e81ce7dde7bde90705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e40",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……没什么大不了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c30909e7d8e7dde7bdefa5e7b5e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e53",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "话说回来、巴尼、出击准备好了吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81fe7edef52efcf02e85be89602efbee7cce87ae877e7c7e7bae8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e86",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、是、是的！出击准备、已经完毕！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7b602e7b6e7b4ef97efbee7cce87ae87702ef3ae8b7e87eea2cef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ebb",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……好！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c7ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ec3",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "独眼巨人小队、出击！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8eee90bea25efb2e83ee7c902efbee7ccef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x414e",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟、竟然要到此为止了吗……！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2c02ef2ce7efef2ae7d7e7cae7c1e869e7bae8020909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x418e",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不好！旗舰一旦被击毁、那可就……",
