  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x42db",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "与他们一战、检验一下你亲手培养的部队{00}实力、也不错",
   "zh_hex": "15e832e80ce7bbefb6ef2802ee40ea99efb6ef4de7b8e894ef66edfeec0be7b4ef70e7c900e87fefb002e7c0e7b5e88500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4300",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特殊演习』、即可与{00}他们交战",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfed7bea2feab60d02e855e7c4e83200e80ce7bbe861ef28000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4325",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4349",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也希望你能尽情地玩到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e87be965e7b8e7c6e8f2e88bef63e970e7d7e8c5e7fe00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x43c2",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你一路陪着我这个不太可靠的舰长",
