  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x45be",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beef66e8d2e9160de7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x45d4",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、虽说我们主天使队的战斗已到此结{00}束……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e8b8e7edefcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4ef28e7ffef3ae7d7e7cae86800e89509090000000000"
